title: TMNT.Turtles.In.Time.ReShelled.PSN.PS3-DUPLEX
description:
Hi, second upload! xD

Install the main file, then the crack or the file with the short name according to your CFW. I used the second one for my Rogero 4.55 CFW; I included both just in case (both files are 8.61 MB in size).

Enjoy and ask for help if it didn't work with you (I finished the whole game and it worked like a charm).

If you happen to install the wrong crack, just delete the game and then install again!
